    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=MvPolynomial.IsHomogeneous\">https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=MvPolynomial.IsHomogeneous</a> finds 44 declarations that mention <code>IsHomogeneous</code> and none seem relevant</p>",
